GPU Commands :
 To dispaly the details and the cmpute processes use the following command
	$ pip install nvitop
	$ run the command "nvitop" in the terminal to moniter  the GPUs
	$ or use this command to moniter the GPUs "watch -d -n 0.5 nvidia-smi"
CPU commands :
 To moniter the details of the cpu of the server
 	$ pip install bpytop
	$ bpytop in the terminal 
